org.pititom.core is a usefull java tools provider

Provides :
        - stream stack editor
        - generic event transmitter and handler
        - extensible messenger

Details of modules :
	- org.pititom.core
	- org.pititom.core.args4jâ€¯          -> requires org.kohsuke.args4j, org.pititom.core
	- org.pititom.core.event
	- org.pititom.core.logging          -> requires org.pititom.core.event
	- org.pititom.core.messenger        -> requires org.kohsuke.args4j, org.pititom.core, org.pititom.core.event, org.pititom.core.args4j, org.pititom.core.logging
	- org.pititom.core.messenger.stream -> requires org.kohsuke.args4j, org.pititom.core, org.pititom.core.event, org.pititom.core.stream, org.pititom.core.stream.editor, org.pititom.core.logging, org.pititom.core.messenger
	- org.pititom.core.stream           -> requires org.kohsuke.args4j, org.pititom.core, org.pititom.core.args4j
	- org.pititom.core.stream.editor    -> requires org.kohsuke.args4j, org.pititom.core, org.pititom.core.args4j

See test directory for samples
